_:N3fb579f650324e64bcc402546ab5a6da <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Keir Mather was appointed Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State in the Department for Transport on 7 September 2025.</p>\n\n<p>He was previously Assistant Whip, House of Commons between 10 July 2024 and 7 September 2025. He was elected as the MP for Selby in July 2024.</p>\n" .
